snippet.title: Junxions Announcement Trailer: An indie city building game about traffic
snippet.description:
Become a traffic engineer with an upcoming indie sandbox simulation game for PC.

Building roads and intersections completely reimagined, with traffic simulated by powerful AI.

Wishlist now on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1447250/Junxions/

For more information visit
https://junxions.com

Become a part of our community!
https://discord.gg/64XQQB874E
https://reddit.com/r/Junxions

Music: Accelerated by Miami Nights 1984
